text: Mavlyutovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Mavlyutovsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 23 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Mishkino, 4 km from Tatarbayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Mavlyutovo, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
